data.description: Welcome to 10 Mill Stream Drive, a meticulously maintained and updated Willow Hill model home nestled in the serene countryside of Berks County, right on the Chester County Line. Situated on one of the largest lots in the Mill Stream development, this property boasts mature landscaping and a tranquil environment.  As you step inside, you are greeted by a two-story foyer adorned with a neutral paint scheme and hardwood floors that extend throughout the entire first floor. The stunning staircase, featuring sleek black wrought iron spindles, adds a touch of elegance to the entryway. To the left, the formal dining room awaits, complete with crown molding, chair rail, wainscoting, and a centered chandelier, perfect for hosting dinner parties and gatherings. On the right, a versatile front living room flex space offers endless possibilities as an office, playroom, or additional living area. Entertaining is a breeze with the kitchen conveniently located off the dining room. The spacious kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a large island with seating, white cabinetry, granite countertops, a corner pantry, and an eat-in dining area with sliders leading to the outdoor oasis. With the kitchen overlooking the family room, hosting and socializing become seamless. Continuing on the main level, you'll find a powder room, first-floor laundry, and a large closet for added convenience. Ascend the open staircase to discover the primary suite, complete with a generous walk-in closet and a private ensuite bathroom featuring a large stall shower. Three additional bedrooms, each bathed in natural light and offering ample closet space, along with a centrally located hall bathroom, provide plenty of space for family and guests.  Let your imagination soar in the daylight basement, flooded with natural sunlight, offering endless possibilities for recreation or additional living space. An oversized two-car garage with a storage area provides plenty of room for vehicles and belongings.  Outside, look forward to relaxing summer evenings on the large composite deck, overlooking the expansive lot with plenty of privacy and mature landscaping. The convenient location offers easy access to the PA Turnpike,  as well as routes 322, 176 and 422. Don't miss your chance to make this impeccable home yours and experience countryside living at its finest at 10 Mill Stream Drive. Schedule your showing today!
